PrecisEnactment of the INDUSTRIAL DESIGN REGULATIONS which (a) enact the Regulations under the sole responsibility of the Governor in Council, (b) provide clarification as to the manner in which documents should be submitted to the Canadian Intellectual Property Office, and (c) set out the requirements regarding filing dates, priority filings, "registered proprietors", notifications of appointments of agents, third party protests to a registration, postal addresses, paper size and copies, effective December 15, 1999.

precis:
Enactment of the INDUSTRIAL DESIGN REGULATIONS which (a) enact the
Regulations under the sole responsibility of the Governor in Council,
(b) provide clarification as to the manner in which documents should be
submitted to the Canadian Intellectual Property Office, and (c) set out the
requirements regarding filing dates, priority filings, "registered
proprietors", notifications of appointments of agents, third party protests
to a registration, postal addresses, paper size and copies, effective
December 15, 1999.
